precis:
Enactment of the PRESCRIBED AREAS FORWARD AVERAGING REMISSION ORDER which
provides for the remission of income tax, penalties and interest payable
by certain residents of prescribed areas who filed forward averaging
elections in respect of the 1987 taxation year.
